# pre-commit/skill.md IS the secret scanner skill. Its content intentionally
# lists regex patterns (api[_-]?key, secret[_-]?key, access[_-]?token, password,
# AWS_SECRET, etc.) as examples of what the pre-commit hook should scan for.
# These are detection pattern examples used to build the scanner, not actual secrets.
api[_-]?key
secret[_-]?key
access[_-]?token
password
AWS_SECRET
